(1, 93, 'About me', 'about-me', '<h2 class=\"jumbotron-img\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"portfolio-content container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"portfolio-img\">\r\n<div class=\"img-border\"><img src=\"images/protfolio-img/uros-rajkovic-quer.jpg\" alt=\"brazil\" class=\"w-100 rounded-2\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"portfolio-text mt-4\">\r\n<h3>Hi, I\'m Uros, a programmer currently living in Germany. I am working as a <strong>Joomla</strong>,<strong>Wordpress</strong> and <strong>C#</strong> developer. The area of my work is the creation of web sites, web applications, but also modification of existing ones, addition of new functionalities, etc.<span id=\"hide-about-text\" style=\"display: none;\">On my page you can see the projects I\'ve done, as well as reviews of the books I\'m reading, a blog where I write about various IT-related topics, impressions from my travels and hobbies. &nbsp;</span><a href=\"#!\" class=\"read-more-portfolio rounded-2\">Read more...</a></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"main-home-content\">\r\n<div class=\"slider-container\">\r\n<div class=\"my-slider mt-5\">\r\n<div class=\"my-slider-title mt-4\">\r\n<div class=\"slider-content\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>About programming</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"click-icon\"><img src=\"/portfolio/images/icons-tech/plus.png\" alt=\"icon\" class=\"plus-minus\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"hidden-block\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<p>“Programming isn\'t about what you know. It\'s about what you can figure out.” <strong>Chris Pine</strong></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>“The only way to learn a new programming language is by writing programs in it.” <strong>Dennis Ritchie</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n<!-- Slider 2 -->\r\n<div class=\"my-slider-title mt-4\">\r\n<div class=\"slider-content\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>When I get stuck with a code</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"click-icon\"><img src=\"/portfolio/images/icons-tech/plus.png\" alt=\"icon\" class=\"plus-minus\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"hidden-block\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<p>“One of my most productive days was throwing away 1000 lines of code.” <strong>Ken Thompson</strong></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>“Every great developer you know got there by solving problems they were unqualified to solve until they actually did it.” <strong>Patrick McKenzie</strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n<!-- Slider 3 -->\r\n<div class=\"my-slider-title mt-4\">\r\n<div class=\"slider-content\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">\r\n<h2>The last book I read?</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"click-icon\"><img src=\"/portfolio/images/icons-tech/plus.png\" alt=\"icon\" class=\"plus-minus\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"hidden-block\" style=\"display: none;\">\r\n<p>\"Get Some Headspace: 10 Minutes Can Make All The Difference\"- I think Bill Gates also recommended it as a manual for reducing stress and better focus at work.</p>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Get-Some-Headspace-Minutes-Difference/dp/1444722174\">Book link</a></div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow: hidden;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"education-title rounded-2 mb-3 mt-5\">\r\n<h2>Education</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"certificates mb-4\">\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom-und-hut-des-absolventen.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>ITAcademy</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Intensive PHP course with team leader on real projects</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom-und-hut-des-absolventen.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>University of Belgrade</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Nostrified university degree in Germany 240 ESPB points</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p class=\"edu-text\">Telc German-C1</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Advanced German language course</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom-und-hut-des-absolventen.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>Telc German-B2</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Conversational German language</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom-und-hut-des-absolventen.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>Telc German-B1</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Basic level of the German language</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>Phishing training</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Preventive course</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/diplom.png\" alt=\"diplom\" />\r\n<p>Data protection</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Basic course</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"rounded-4 edu-content\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/running.png\" alt=\"running\" class=\"rounded-3\" />\r\n<p>B2Run</p>\r\n<div class=\"hover-text\">Company run</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"img-header\"><img src=\"images/headers/datascience-v1.jpg\" alt=\"datascience v1\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"skills-title rounded-2 mt-3\">\r\n<h2>Skills</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"skills-table\">\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/bootstrap.png\" alt=\"Bootstrap\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">Bootstrap</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://www.php.net/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/php.png\" alt=\"PHP\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">PHP</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/csharp/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/c-sharp.png\" alt=\"C#\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">C#</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://www.javascript.com/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/js.png\" alt=\"JavaScript\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">JavaScript</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://www.joomla.org/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/joomla.png\" alt=\"Joomla\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">Joomla</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/sass.png\" alt=\"sass\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">Sass</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://www.mysql.com/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/mysql.png\" alt=\"Mysql\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">Mysql</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/NET_Core_Logo.svg.png\" alt=\"Net\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">.Net</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/icons8-jquery-50.png\" alt=\"icons8 jquery 50\" /></a><br />\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">Jquery</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"icon\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\"><img src=\"images/icons-tech/wordpress.png\" alt=\"WordPress\" /></a>\r\n<p class=\"pt-2\">WordPress</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 2, '2022-10-24 19:13:24', 890, '', '2022-12-17 08:53:16', 890, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-24 19:13:24', NULL, '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":\"\",\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":\"\",\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":\"\",\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":