(274, 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1', 'index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1:about-me&catid=2', 'About me', ' Hi, I\'m Uros, a programmer currently living in Germany. I am working as a Joomla,Wordpress and C# developer. The area of my work is the creation of web sites, web applications, but also modification of existing ones, addition of new functionalities, etc.On my page you can see the projects I\'ve done, as well as reviews of the books I\'m reading, a blog where I write about various IT-related topics, impressions from my travels and hobbies. Read more... About programming “Programming isn\'t about what you know. It\'s about what you can figure out.” Chris Pine “The only way to learn a new programming language is by writing programs in it.” Dennis Ritchie When I get stuck with a code “One of my most productive days was throwing away 1000 lines of code.” Ken Thompson “Every great developer you know got there by solving problems they were unqualified to solve until they actually did it.” Patrick McKenzie The last book I read? \"Get Some Headspace: 10 Minutes Can Make All The Difference\"- I think Bill Gates also recommended it as a manual for reducing stress and better focus at work. Book link Education ITAcademy Intensive PHP course with team leader on real projects University of Belgrade Nostrified university degree in Germany 240 ESPB points Telc German-C1 Advanced German language course Telc German-B2 Conversational German language Telc German-B1 Basic level of the German language Phishing training Preventive course Data protection Basic course B2Run Company run Skills Bootstrap PHP C# JavaScript Joomla Sass Mysql .Net Jquery WordPress ', '2022-12-17 08:53:16', '8eecf0cc6c95237a5bc816febb14ee37', 1, 1, 1, '*', '2022-10-24 19:13:24', NULL, '2022-10-24 19:13:24', NULL, 0, 0, 3, );
