" class=\\\"width-25\\\" loading=\\\"lazy\\\" data-path=\\\"local-images:\\/blog-headers\\/ThoughtLeadership_shutterstock_109952966.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201cStartup se nabave nicim drugim do pronalazenjem poslovnog modela\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201cMesec dana ili tri, to je kao vecnost u Dolini\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201cNajveci rizik pri otvaranju firmi je da stvorite nesto stov ec postoji\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eKreativnost nije nista drugo do sposobnost da se ide novim putevima\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eMenadzeri u klasicnim firmama razmisljaju u analogijama. Sve sto cine ili ne cine izvode iz predjasnjeg. Takvim razmisljanjem oni firme udaljavaju od inovatnog\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eSamo sest nedelja je dovoljno najvecem broju startap firmi od ideje do prvog proizvoda\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eNi mi sami ne znamo sta je vazno. To samo zna korisnik\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eSamo onaj ko uspe da ponudi online zahteve kupcima ima sansu da prezivi\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">O komunikaciji<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201ePalo Altu nema vise fiksne telefone\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eVeze su vaznije od novca\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201ePoreklo, pol, religija, godine \\u2013 za takve stvari dolina je slepa\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201cPrevise je onih koji kradu vreme\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2>&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">O buducnosti<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eKarijera bez osnovnog razumevanja c++ u 2030 godini bice isto toliko nemoguca kao sto je danas nemoguca bez znanja engleskog jezika\\u201c<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">\\u201eDecu saljemo u potencijalno neprijateljski svet u kome ce dominirati algoritmi, ali im ne saopstavamo sta su algoritmi\\u201c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.amazon.de\\/-\\/en\\/gp\\/product\\/B01M4HA7C8\\/ref=dbs_a_def_rwt_bibl_vppi_i4\\\">Book-link<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2022-12-08 18:22:04\",\"created_by\":\"890\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2022-12-10 22:19:41\",\"modified_by\":890,\"checked_out\":890,\"checked_out_time\":\"2022-12-10 22:18:55\",\"publish_up\":\"2022-12-08 18:22:04\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/Silicon-Valley-Mindset.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/Silicon-Valley-Mindset.jpg?width=1360&height=979\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/Silicon-Valley-Mindset.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/Silicon-Valley-Mindset.jpg?width=1360&height=979\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":40,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":197,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(204, 'com_content.article.16', '', '2022-12-15 20:31:34', 890, 7976, '5ab45f61de67cdee89c9af52e2a005d3c2b971eb', '{\"id\":\"16\",\"asset_id\":112,\"title\":\"Tasks from the Google job interview\",\"alias\":\"tasks-from-the-google-job-interview\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Primetio sam da jedna od interesantinih tema su intervjui i zadaci za developere iz velikih tech korporacija.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>U tom smisliu Google je mozda jedno od najpozeljnih mesta za vecinu programera pa mnogi okusavaju svoju srecu sa njihovom procesom zaposljavanja.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Na intervju su uglavnom rade tri zadataka, al u ovom tekstu cu prikazati samo jedan.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Zadatak:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dat je sortiran niz od N celobrojnih elemenata. Potrebno je prebrojati koliko se puta neki zadati broj pojavljuje.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Trivijalno re\\u0161enje je da se jednim prolazom kroz niz u linearnoj slo\\u017eenosti prebroje sva pojavljivanja ovog elementa. Avaj, sa takvim znanjem verovatno ne\\u0107ete pro\\u0107i intervjue, jer je ovo re\\u0161enje neefikasno. Po\\u0161to je niz sortiran, name\\u0107e se ideja da upotrebimo&nbsp;<strong>binarnu pretragu<\\/strong>. Kada bismo proveravali da li neki element uop\\u0161te postoji u nizu, ovo bi se lako odradilo u logaritamskoj slo\\u017eenosti, ali na\\u0161 zadatak je ne\\u0161to te\\u017ei, jer zapravo tra\\u017eimo du\\u017einu dela niza gde se ovaj element javlja.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Prvi na\\u010din sa binarnom pretragom jeste da prona\\u0111emo tra\\u017eeni element, i da nakon toga iteriramo levo i desno od njega i prebrojimo pojavljivanja. Me\\u0111utim, u najgorem slu\\u010daju ovaj pristup ima linearnu slo\\u017eenost, jer se mo\\u017ee desiti da se u celom nizu nalazi samo taj element.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ovo \\u0107emo re\\u0161iti upotrebom ne\\u0161to druga\\u010dije binarne pretrage koja tra\\u017ei&nbsp;<strong>poslednji element<\\/strong>&nbsp;u nizu koji je&nbsp;<strong>strogo manji od X<\\/strong>. Sa ovakvim algoritmom \\u0107emo mo\\u0107i da na\\u0111emo krajeve intervala koji sadr\\u017ei tra\\u017eeni broj X:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>da bismo na\\u0161li po\\u010detak intervala, pozva\\u0107emo binarnu pretragu sa parametrom X, i kao njenu povratnu vrednost \\u0107emo dobiti prvi element levo od podniza koji nas interesuje, pa njegov indeks jednostavno uve\\u0107amo za 1<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>da bismo na\\u0161li kraj intervala, pozva\\u0107emo binarnu pretragu sa parametrom X+1, i povratna vrednost \\u0107e predstavljati upravo kraj intervala<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Ideja je veoma jednostavna, ali problem mo\\u017ee predstavljati realizacija koju bi sigurno zatra\\u017eili od vas na intervjuu, jer postoji dosta posebnih slu\\u010dajeva na koje treba obratiti pa\\u017enju:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako taj element ne postoji?<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako se podniz nalazi na samom po\\u010detku niza?<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako se podniz nalazi na samom kraju niza?<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Sledi C++ k\\u00f4d koji uspe\\u0161no re\\u0161ava zadati problem.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>int&nbsp;countOccurancesInSortedArray(int&nbsp;*array,&nbsp;int&nbsp;len,&nbsp;int&nbsp;x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Special cases<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(len == 0) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Empty array<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(x &lt; array[0] || x &gt; array[len-1]) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Number definitely not present in array<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Find the end of the interval<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;right = findLastElementSmallerThan(x+1, array, 0, len-1);<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(array[right] != x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Element does not exist, since the end of the interval isn\'t X<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ No need to go over the entire array, just left of the end of the interval<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Also, if the array starts with X, the return index is -1<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ We need to pass the appropriate parameters, i.e. \\\"-1\\\" and \\\"right\\\"<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;left = findLastElementSmallerThan(x, array, -1, right) + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Result<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;right - left + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>int&nbsp;findLastElementSmallerThan(int&nbsp;x,&nbsp;int&nbsp;*array,&nbsp;int&nbsp;left,&nbsp;int&nbsp;right) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(left &lt; right) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;mid = (right == 0) ? 0 : (left + right) \\/ 2 + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(array[mid] &gt;= x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;right = mid - 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;&nbsp;{<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;left = mid;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;right;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>}<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2022-12-07 22:26:49\",\"created_by\":\"890\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2022-12-15 20:31:34\",\"modified_by\":890,\"checked_out\":890,\"checked_out_time\":\"2022-12-15 20:30:17\",\"publish_up\":\"2022-12-07 22:26:49\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg?width=1323&height=744\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg?width=1323&height=744\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":17,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":55,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(205, 'com_content.article.16', '', '2022-12-15 20:32:21', 890, 7965, 'd99cf83d439ede93f2ec9252657188e5d9196b2d', '{\"id\":\"16\",\"asset_id\":112,\"title\":\"Tasks from the Google job interview\",\"alias\":\"tasks-from-the-google-job-interview\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Primetio sam da jedna od interesantinih tema su intervjui i zadaci za developere iz velikih tech korporacija. U tom smisliu Google je mozda jedno od najpozeljnih mesta za vecinu programera pa mnogi okusavaju svoju srecu sa njihovom procesom zaposljavanja.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p>Na intervju su uglavnom rade tri zadataka, al u ovom tekstu cu prikazati samo jedan.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Zadatak:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Dat je sortiran niz od N celobrojnih elemenata. Potrebno je prebrojati koliko se puta neki zadati broj pojavljuje.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Trivijalno re\\u0161enje je da se jednim prolazom kroz niz u linearnoj slo\\u017eenosti prebroje sva pojavljivanja ovog elementa. Avaj, sa takvim znanjem verovatno ne\\u0107ete pro\\u0107i intervjue, jer je ovo re\\u0161enje neefikasno. Po\\u0161to je niz sortiran, name\\u0107e se ideja da upotrebimo&nbsp;<strong>binarnu pretragu<\\/strong>. Kada bismo proveravali da li neki element uop\\u0161te postoji u nizu, ovo bi se lako odradilo u logaritamskoj slo\\u017eenosti, ali na\\u0161 zadatak je ne\\u0161to te\\u017ei, jer zapravo tra\\u017eimo du\\u017einu dela niza gde se ovaj element javlja.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Prvi na\\u010din sa binarnom pretragom jeste da prona\\u0111emo tra\\u017eeni element, i da nakon toga iteriramo levo i desno od njega i prebrojimo pojavljivanja. Me\\u0111utim, u najgorem slu\\u010daju ovaj pristup ima linearnu slo\\u017eenost, jer se mo\\u017ee desiti da se u celom nizu nalazi samo taj element.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ovo \\u0107emo re\\u0161iti upotrebom ne\\u0161to druga\\u010dije binarne pretrage koja tra\\u017ei&nbsp;<strong>poslednji element<\\/strong>&nbsp;u nizu koji je&nbsp;<strong>strogo manji od X<\\/strong>. Sa ovakvim algoritmom \\u0107emo mo\\u0107i da na\\u0111emo krajeve intervala koji sadr\\u017ei tra\\u017eeni broj X:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>da bismo na\\u0161li po\\u010detak intervala, pozva\\u0107emo binarnu pretragu sa parametrom X, i kao njenu povratnu vrednost \\u0107emo dobiti prvi element levo od podniza koji nas interesuje, pa njegov indeks jednostavno uve\\u0107amo za 1<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>da bismo na\\u0161li kraj intervala, pozva\\u0107emo binarnu pretragu sa parametrom X+1, i povratna vrednost \\u0107e predstavljati upravo kraj intervala<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Ideja je veoma jednostavna, ali problem mo\\u017ee predstavljati realizacija koju bi sigurno zatra\\u017eili od vas na intervjuu, jer postoji dosta posebnih slu\\u010dajeva na koje treba obratiti pa\\u017enju:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako taj element ne postoji?<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako se podniz nalazi na samom po\\u010detku niza?<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>\\u0160ta ako se podniz nalazi na samom kraju niza?<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>Sledi C++ k\\u00f4d koji uspe\\u0161no re\\u0161ava zadati problem.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>int&nbsp;countOccurancesInSortedArray(int&nbsp;*array,&nbsp;int&nbsp;len,&nbsp;int&nbsp;x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Special cases<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(len == 0) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Empty array<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(x &lt; array[0] || x &gt; array[len-1]) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Number definitely not present in array<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Find the end of the interval<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;right = findLastElementSmallerThan(x+1, array, 0, len-1);<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(array[right] != x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Element does not exist, since the end of the interval isn\'t X<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;0;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ No need to go over the entire array, just left of the end of the interval<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Also, if the array starts with X, the return index is -1<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ We need to pass the appropriate parameters, i.e. \\\"-1\\\" and \\\"right\\\"<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;left = findLastElementSmallerThan(x, array, -1, right) + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/\\/ Result<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;right - left + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>int&nbsp;findLastElementSmallerThan(int&nbsp;x,&nbsp;int&nbsp;*array,&nbsp;int&nbsp;left,&nbsp;int&nbsp;right) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;while&nbsp;(left &lt; right) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;mid = (right == 0) ? 0 : (left + right) \\/ 2 + 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;(array[mid] &gt;= x) {<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;right = mid - 1;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;&nbsp;{<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;left = mid;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;right;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>}<\\/p>\",\"state\":\"1\",\"catid\":8,\"created\":\"2022-12-07 22:26:49\",\"created_by\":\"890\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2022-12-15 20:32:21\",\"modified_by\":890,\"checked_out\":890,\"checked_out_time\":\"2022-12-15 20:31:34\",\"publish_up\":\"2022-12-07 22:26:49\",\"publish_down\":null,\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg?width=1323&height=744\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg#joomlaImage:\\\\\\/\\\\\\/local-images\\\\\\/blog-headers\\\\\\/cf20b634238ded541edda338e0cb6888_google.hero.jpg?width=1323&height=744\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":18,\"ordering\":0,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":1,\"hits\":56,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0);
